    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "adjust the border radius for the main components of the interface, such as cards, buttons and inputs. increasing the radius can give a softer and more rounded look to the UI, while decreasing it can create a sharper and more angular appearance.",
      "target": "调整界面主要组件（如卡片、按钮和输入框）的边框圆角。增加圆角可以使界面外观更柔和、更圆润，而减小圆角则可以创造更锐利、更棱角分明的外观。"
    },
