    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "an experimental feature that applies a frosted glass effect to the main components of the interface, such as notes, sidebars and ribbons. this is designed to work together with the workspace transparency settings, but it can be used on its own as well. enabling this will add a significant amount of extra processing load to your system, so it's not recommended for low-end devices.",
